channel.title: How do you add a donater or staff island?
channel.description: I want to add an island for donaters and staff but how do you do it... so staff can type ::staff and get to the island...or donater do ::donaterisland for donater island...

item.title: How do you add a donater or staff island?
item.dc:creator: @PushedPrawn PushedPrawn
item.description:
@PushedPrawn wrote:

[quote=“hmong95, post:1, topic:309315”]I want to add an island for donaters and staff but how do you do it…
so staff can type ::staff and get to the island…or donater do ::donaterisland for donater island…[/quote]
Well, you can’t “make” a donater island or any island, really. Unless you really know what you’re doing.

BUT… if you find an already made island, you can make a teleport command “::donator” or “::staff”

Ex;

  if (command.equalsIgnoreCase("home"))
            if (teleblock == true) {
                sM("Hah, biatchh... You're TELEBLOCKED! Don't try dat shit!");
            } else {
              toX = 3094;
               toY = 3243;
            }

Or something like that.

That’s for Delta, though.
